stdout:
start:
	docker run --net mongo-net --ip $(ip) --name $(name) -d mongo-dev --replSet "poly" --bind_ip=$(ip),127.0.0.1

stop:
	docker kill $(name)
	docker rm $(name)

start-all:
	docker network create --subnet=172.18.0.0/24 mongo-net
	make start ip="172.18.0.10" name="server1"
	make start ip="172.18.0.11" name="server2"
	make start ip="172.18.0.12" name="server3"

stop-all:
	make stop name="server1"
	make stop name="server2"
	make stop name="server3"
	docker network rm mongo-net

connect:
	docker exec -t -i $(name) sh -c "mongo"
